Retry #6326

Should we remove `Mathlib.Algebra.Order.Ring.Canonical` from `Mathlib.Algebra.Order.Ring.Nat`?

```
.\.\.\.\Mathlib\Algebra\Order\Ring\Nat.lean:
  remove #[Mathlib.Algebra.Order.Group.Nat, Mathlib.Algebra.Order.Ring.Canonical]
  add #[Mathlib.Algebra.Ring.Parity, Mathlib.Algebra.Order.Ring.Defs]
  instead
    import [Mathlib.Algebra.Order.Sub.Canonical, Mathlib.Algebra.Order.Group.Nat] in Mathlib.Data.Nat.Cast.Order
    import [Mathlib.Algebra.Order.Group.Nat] in Mathlib.Data.Rat.Lemmas
    import [Mathlib.Algebra.Order.Sub.Canonical, Mathlib.Algebra.Order.Group.Nat] in Mathlib.Data.PNat.Basic
    import [Mathlib.Algebra.Order.Sub.Canonical, Mathlib.Algebra.Order.Group.Nat] in Mathlib.Data.Set.Pointwise.Basic
    import [Mathlib.Algebra.Order.Group.Nat] in Mathlib.Data.Nat.GCD.Basic
    import [Mathlib.Algebra.Order.Sub.Canonical, Mathlib.Algebra.Order.Group.Nat] in Mathlib.Data.Nat.SuccPred
    import [Mathlib.Algebra.Order.Ring.Canonical] in Mathlib.SetTheory.Cardinal.Basic
    import [Mathlib.Algebra.Order.Ring.Canonical] in Mathlib.Data.Set.Semiring
    import [Mathlib.Algebra.Order.Sub.Canonical] in Mathlib.Data.Nat.Prime
    import [Mathlib.Algebra.Order.Group.Nat] in Mathlib.Data.Nat.WithBot
    import [Mathlib.Algebra.Order.Group.Nat] in Mathlib.Data.Nat.MaxPowDiv
    import [Mathlib.Algebra.Order.Group.Nat] in Mathlib.Algebra.Tropical.Basic
    import [Mathlib.Algebra.Order.Ring.Canonical] in Mathlib.Combinatorics.SimpleGraph.Regularity.Equitabilise
    import [Mathlib.Algebra.Order.Ring.Canonical, Mathlib.Algebra.Order.Group.Nat] in Mathlib.Combinatorics.SetFamily.HarrisKleitman
    import [Mathlib.Algebra.Order.Sub.Canonical, Mathlib.Algebra.Order.Group.Nat] in Mathlib.Data.Nat.Upto
    import [Mathlib.Algebra.Order.Group.Nat] in Mathlib.Data.Bool.Count
    import [Mathlib.Algebra.Order.Ring.Canonical, Mathlib.Algebra.Order.Group.Nat] in Mathlib.Data.Nat.Dist
    import [Mathlib.Algebra.Order.Group.Nat] in Mathlib.SetTheory.Lists
```
